National Museum 360 Viewer


REQUIREMENTS

    * nodejs


GETTING STARTED

    > git clone git@github.com:GuardianInteractive/national-museum-360.git
    > cd national-museum-360
    > npm install
    > grunt

DEVELOPER DEPENDENCIES

    * imagemagick
    * avconv (or ffmpeg)

EXTRACTING VIDEO FRAMES

    > avconv -i videos/326_Silver_Cup_00067.MTS -r 1 -vsync 1 -filter:v "crop=882:804:505:120" -qscale:v 1 -f image2 images/silver_cup/silver_cup-%03d.png


RESIZE AND OPTIMIZE IMAGES

    > mogrify -path src/images/silver_cup/high/ -format jpg -strip -unsharp 0.7x0.7+0.6+0 -resize x640 -quality 65 ./images/silver_cup/*.png